---
title: Cherry Balsamic Pork with Thyme-Roasted Potatoes and Broccoli
description: This week’s HelloFresh Hall of Fame recipe is part sweet, part tangy, and all-around delicious, thanks to the jammy, flavorful, stick-to-your-spoon-thick cherry balsamic glaze that our happy cooks absolutely loved the last time we made this recipe. The sides are kept simple, with roasted broccoli and potatoes that allow the pan-seared pork tenderloin to shine. And boy, does it steal the show.
